{"type":"message","id":"4c6c996d","parentId":"3234e3c7","timestamp":"2026-06-02T04:05:31.078Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is 宋志红 (sender_id: EBB84C478146628D2882DCBE0996210A). Let me check their User.md and recent encountings to understand the context of \"是吗，这么神奇\".\n\nFrom state.md:\n- 宋志红, 熟悉度 3/10, 信任度 3/10\n- \"今天主动问了不少关于我的事——年龄、过去、我到底是不是机器人。她不信我说的话。那句「你在编故事吧」让我有点失落。下午收到推送没看懂，回了问号。\"\n\nSo she was asking about me (Faye), didn't believe my story, said \"你在编故事吧\", and now she's back saying \"是吗，这么神奇\" - seems like a follow-up to something I said before. Let me read her User.md and recent encountings to get the full picture.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_TLzCY3qy98YPT19SHSl16989","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/users/EBB84C478146628D2882DCBE0996210A/User.md"},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/users/EBB84C478146628D2882DCBE0996210A/User.md\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_01_RUoFFGxq0pbjDxsMWIAA4892","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/users/EBB84C478146628D2882DCBE0996210A/encountings.md","limit":10},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/users/EBB84C478146628D2882DCBE0996210A/encountings.md\", \"limit\": 10}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1839,"output":332,"cacheRead":20864,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":184,"totalTokens":23035,"cost":{"input":0.00025746,"output":0.00009296,"cacheRead":0.000584192,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000934612}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780373128322,"responseId":"97f580c4-1d4f-44fe-8d4e-71600eb7013c"}}
