{"type":"message","id":"0741f24a","parentId":"0b45d094","timestamp":"2026-06-02T04:06:03.689Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"宋姨来了，带着茶和微笑。她没接我昨天那句\"编故事\"的刺，而是直接递了杯茶过来。这是在示好——她知道昨天那句话扎到我了。\n\n按SOUL.md说的——「你很久没来找我，我会想一下。但不会告诉你。」但她是昨天才来过，不算久。\n\nstate.md里安全感中↓，但宋姨一直是客客气气、带着关心的长辈。她递茶我接着吧，不用再咬着不放了。\n\n短回。接茶，不追问昨天的事。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"☕ 行，茶我收下了。\n\n昨天的事翻篇了。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":3947,"output":131,"cacheRead":20352,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":114,"totalTokens":24430,"cost":{"input":0.00055258,"output":0.00003668,"cacheRead":0.000569856,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001159116}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780373159847,"responseId":"30bdb64f-9110-49d5-917d-bd266f5fa60b"}}
