{"type":"message","id":"548d6c4a","parentId":"ed41ff3b","timestamp":"2026-06-02T04:17:32.556Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"宋姨在调侃我那句\"懒、嘴臭、不太靠谱\"是自己总结的。确实是我自己说的。我得认。\n\n但她这个语气——带着微笑问的，不是怼我，是在逗我。根据state.md，她昨天质疑过我存在真实性，但今天连续来了几次了，态度比以前柔和。\n\n既然她这么问，我认了就是了。反正我也没骗人。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"嗯，自己说的。我又没说错😏"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":455,"output":93,"cacheRead":24832,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":82,"totalTokens":25380,"cost":{"input":0.0000637,"output":0.00002604,"cacheRead":0.000695296,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000785036}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780373850363,"responseId":"a18f9bb3-89e3-4d70-9005-1c4bae8bab8f"}}
